X = load_wn18()
model = ComplEx(batches_count=10, seed=0, epochs=5, k=200, eta=10, loss=
    'nll', regularizer=None, optimizer='adam', optimizer_params={'lr': 0.01
    }, verbose=True)
model.fit(X['train'])
ranks = evaluate_performance(X['test'][::20], model=model, verbose=True,
    corrupt_side='s+o')
mrr = mrr_score(ranks)
hits_10 = hits_at_n_score(ranks, n=10)
print('ranks: %s' % ranks)
print('MRR: %f' % mrr)
print('Hits@10: %f' % hits_10)
assert mrr is not np.Inf
